      "text": "DEPARTMENT OF INFORMATION TECHNOLOGY SHRI GOVINDRAM SEKSARIA INSTITUTE OF SCIENCE AND TECHNOLOGY INTERNSHIP REPORT ON Full Stack Development Submitted by: - Sourabh Malviya Enrollment No. 0801IT231130 Course Duration: 10/06/2025 to 25/010/2025 Check out the live project: https://wanderlust-86hv.onrender.com 1 2 Acknowledgement I would like to express my sincere gratitude to Apna College for providing me with the opportunity to enroll in the Sigma Full Stack Web Development Course. The course has been a valuable learning experience that helped me gain both theoretical knowledge and practical skills in technologies such as HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React, Node.js, Express, and MongoDB. I am especially thankful to Shraddha Khapra Ma am and the entire Apna College team for their clear explanations, continuous guidance, and well-structured course content that made complex topics easy to understand. I would also like to thank my peers, mentors, and everyone who supported and motivated me",
