      "id": "tmp5z5a47l1_chunk_3-9376f585be614c1b934638451f2227d2",
      "text": "4 Introduction The Sigma Full Stack Web Development Course by Apna College is a comprehensive program designed to help learners build modern, responsive, and dynamic web applications. Through this course, I gained hands-on experience in both frontend and backend development. The course covered essential technologies such as HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React.js, Node.js, Express.js, and MongoDB, along with concepts of APIs, deployment, and version control using Git and GitHub. It provided a clear understanding of how to develop complete web projects from scratch, integrating both client-side and server-side functionalities. This learning journey not only enhanced my technical skills but also strengthened my problem- solving ability, logical thinking, and confidence in building full-stack projects independently. 5 Learning Outcomes During my Course, I gained practical experience in full-stack web development by working on a React and Node.js based contact form project. The key learning outcomes include: 1. Frontend Development with React and JavaScript",
