      "id": "tmp5z5a47l1_chunk_4-aecf2813c2dd42108903c658a7cda196",
      "text": "solving ability, logical thinking, and confidence in building full-stack projects independently. 5 Learning Outcomes During my Course, I gained practical experience in full-stack web development by working on a React and Node.js based contact form project. The key learning outcomes include: 1. Frontend Development with React and JavaScript Developed reusable and maintainable UI components using React functional components and hooks. Applied JavaScript for type safety, improving code reliability and maintainability. Implemented responsive and user-friendly forms with real-time validation and feedback. Utilized CSS for custom styling and enhanced user experience. 2. State and Event Management Managed component state using React s `useState` hook. Handled user input and form submission events efficiently. Implemented loading states and error handling for better UX. 3. Client-Server Communication Used the Fetch API to send and receive data between the frontend and backend. Structured and sent JSON payloads securely to the server.",
