      "id": "tmp5z5a47l1_chunk_8-2a50d4fe2a2d43eaad8805602d657c94",
      "text": "Deployment Tools To host websites and web apps on live servers. Major Project Conclusion The Sigma Full Stack Web Development Course by Apna College has been a highly valuable and enriching learning experience. Throughout this course, I gained a strong foundation in both frontend and backend technologies, learning how to build complete and fully functional web applications. By working with tools such as HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React.js, Node.js, Express.js, and MongoDB, I developed a clear understanding of how different components of a web project work together. The hands-on projects and practical assignments helped me apply theoretical knowledge to real-world scenarios, improving my problem-solving and coding skills. This course has not only enhanced my technical abilities but also boosted my confidence to pursue a career in web development. I am grateful for the guidance, support, and inspiration",
